NATU cannot fly because its wings are not yet fully grown. If your eyes meet with this Pokemon's eyes it will stareback intently at you. But if you move even slightly it will hop away to safety.
NATU has a highly developed jumping ability. The Pokemon flaps and leaps onto tree branches that are taller thangrown-up people to pick at the tree's new shoots.
